name: Leap Into The Sky
description:
Leap Into The Sky is jump high through the fahombo stone. It is Nias culture that mature man has to be jump over the 2 meters high stone successfuly. This art encourage people to achieve their goal. 
    
    The Series of Indonesia Art Culture (From Dance with Leak, The Dancer, Bali Dancer, Yudhistira Lost in Space & Shinta Dance).
